{"word":"σπανίζω","slug":"σπανίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σπανίζω</b></el> <el>(σπᾰνίζω,) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b>of things, <i>to be rare, scarce, scanty</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of persons, <i>to lack</i> or <i>be in want of</i>, <el>τινός</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>;—so in <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ἐσπανίσμεθ' ἀρωγῶν</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>: <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to be in want</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}